race.comment: Many of these are returning to their favourite course. SURREAL ASCOT (9) is one of those who was thereabouts last time on the Sunshine Coast but has a great record here and is ideally drawn. Will either lead or stalk the lead and is expected to go close. FARNBOROUGH (2) is a former Freedman Victorian who is having first start for a new local yard. Fitter for two trials and goes very well fresh so watch for a betting push closely. THE DEPUTY (4) caught the eye late first up at the Gold Coast and wouldn't have to improve much to be winning here. DON'T DISS AROUND (6) drops back sharply in grade and remains under strong notice.
